<item>
            <title>[LU-3419] lustre-rsync-test test_2b: dbench not running when killed</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3419</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8f8652ea-c797-11e2-9f90-52540035b04c&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sets/8f8652ea-c797-11e2-9f90-52540035b04c&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_2b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Failure in replication; differences found.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There were similar issues reported for interop testing, but this one is hit on zfs with both server and client run b2_4RC2&lt;/p&gt;</description>
